Package: shrike
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: x86-64 / AArch64 ROP gadget finder
 A minimal, dependency-free gadget scanner for ELF64 binaries.
 Recognises pop / mov / arith / stack-pivot / syscall / indirect
 terminators; emits text, JSON, SARIF, pwntools-compatible Python,
 or a register-control index.
